## Tokens
```
[
    TStringStart 0..2 (flags = DOUBLE_QUOTES | T_STRING),
    TStringMiddle 2..6 (flags = DOUBLE_QUOTES | T_STRING),
    Lbrace 6..7,
    Exclamation 7..8,
    Name 8..11,
    Rbrace 11..12,
    TStringMiddle 12..16 (flags = DOUBLE_QUOTES | T_STRING),
    TStringEnd 16..17 (flags = DOUBLE_QUOTES | T_STRING),
    Newline 17..17,
]
```
